sourcesContent: export const isObject=t=>t&&"object"==typeof t;export const renameProp=(t,e,{[t]:o,...r})=>({[e]:o,...r});export const copyObject=t=>isObject(t)?t instanceof Array?[...t]:{...t}:t;export const omitObject=(t,e)=>{if(!isObject(t))return t;if(t instanceof Array)return[...t];const o={...t};return e.forEach((t=>o[t]&&delete o[t])),o};
